    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[Multilingual websites]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>An important aspect in designing a website is localization. Whether the web presence should be just translated to each client's language or culturally fully adapted to the respective target market's locale - OpenCms provides the means necessary to do the job. Get an overview on the different aspects of website localization.</p>]]></content>
